results.cleanName: Structure Deck Saga of Blue Eyes White Dragon 1st Edition
results.name: Structure Deck: Saga of Blue-Eyes White Dragon [1st Edition]

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: This legendary dragon is a powerful engine of destruction. Virtually invincible, very few have faced this awesome creature and lived to tell the tale.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: It's a snowfield-dwelling, giant-ear-sporting, super-acoustic, snowball-shaped mutant dragon! There's no way anybody can escape.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Many of the czars' lost jewels can be found in the scales of this priceless dragon. Its creator remains a mystery, along with how they acquired the imperial treasures. But whosoever finds this dragon has hit the jackpot... whether they know it or not.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: A very beautiful dragon covered with sapphire. It does not like fights, but has incredibly high attack power.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: A Flamvell guardian who commands fire with his will. His magma-hot barrier protects his troops from intruders.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: When this card is targeted for an attack: You can negate the attack, and if you do, change the battle position of this card, then you can Special Summon 1 "Blue-Eyes White Dragon" from your hand, Deck, or Graveyard. During either player's turn, when a card or effect is activated that targets this face-up card (except during the Damage Step): You can Special Summon 1 "Blue-Eyes White Dragon" from your hand, Deck, or Graveyard. You can only use 1 "Maiden with Eyes of Blue" effect per turn, and only once that turn.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: You can target 1 Dragon-Type Normal Monster you control; equip this monster from your hand or your side of the field to that target. If the monster equipped with this card attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage to your opponent. If the equipped monster would be destroyed, destroy this card instead.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: This card is treated as a Normal Monster while face-up on the field or in the Graveyard. While this card is face-up on the field, you can Normal Summon it to have it be treated as an Effect Monster with this effect. // * Once per turn: You can send 1 face-up Spell/Trap Card you control to the Graveyard; destroy all Spell/Trap Cards on the field.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: This card cannot be destroyed by battle with a monster that has the same ATK. When this card is destroyed and sent to the Graveyard, return 1 monster on the field to its owner's hand.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: If your opponent controls a monster and you control no monsters, you can Special Summon this card (from your hand). This card cannot attack during the turn it is Special Summoned this way. When this card is Tributed: Special Summon 1 Dragon-Type Normal Monster from your hand, Deck, or Graveyard, and make its ATK and DEF 0.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Your opponent cannot activate Trap Cards during the Battle Phase.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Once per turn: You can discard 1 card, then target 1 Dragon-Type monster in your Graveyard; add that target to your hand.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: When this card is sent to the Graveyard: Add 1 "Blue-Eyes White Dragon" from your Deck to your hand.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: You can Tribute this face-up card; Special Summon 1 "Blue-Eyes White Dragon" from your hand.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Once per turn: You can discard 1 card, then target 1 Level 7 or higher monster in your Graveyard; add that target to your hand.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: This card can be treated as 2 Tributes for the Tribute Summon of a LIGHT monster.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: During your Main Phase: You can return this card from the field to its owner's hand. During either player's Damage Step, when a face-up LIGHT monster you control battles: You can send this card from your hand to the Graveyard; that monster gains ATK equal to the ATK of the opponent's monster it is battling, until the End Phase.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: When this card is destroyed by battle and sent to the Graveyard: You can Special Summon 1 LIGHT monster with 1500 or less ATK from your Deck, in face-up Attack Position.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Send 1 Dragon-Type monster from your Deck to the Graveyard, then, if that monster in your Graveyard is a Dragon-Type Normal Monster, you can send 1 more Dragon-Type monster from your Deck to the Graveyard. You can only activate 1 "Dragon Shrine" per turn.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Target 1 Dragon-Type Normal Monster in your Graveyard; Special Summon that target. You can only activate 1 "Silver's Cry" per turn.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: If you control a face-up "Blue-Eyes White Dragon": Destroy all monsters your opponent controls. "Blue-Eyes White Dragon" cannot attack the turn you activate this card.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Activate only if you control a face-up Dragon-Type monster. Select 1 Spell or Trap Card on the field, destroy it and inflict 500 damage to its controller.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Return 1 face-up Level 5 or higher Dragon-Type monster you control to the hand, and destroy all Spell and Trap Cards on the field.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Discard 1 Level 8 monster to draw 2 cards.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Discard 1 Dragon-Type Tuner monster with 1000 or less ATK to draw 2 cards.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Send 1 face-up non-Effect Monster you control to the Graveyard to draw 2 cards.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Send 1 monster from your hand to the Graveyard; Special Summon 1 Level 1 monster from your hand or Deck.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Target 1 monster in either player's Graveyard; Special Summon it.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Tribute 2 Dragon-Type monsters; Special Summon 1 Level 8 Dragon-Type monster from your Deck.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Target 1 monster your opponent controls; this turn, if you Tribute a monster, you must Tribute that monster, as if you controlled it. You cannot conduct your Battle Phase the turn you activate this card.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Flip all monsters your opponent controls face-up. This card remains on the field for 3 of your opponent's turns. While this card is face-up on the field, monsters your opponent controls cannot declare an attack.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Activate 1 of these effects. // * Target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; change that target's battle position. // * Tribute 1 monster, then target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls; take control of that target until the End Phase.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Once per turn: You can banish 1 Dragon-Type monster from your Graveyard, then target 1 face-up monster you control; it gains 700 ATK, until the End Phase. (This ATK gain remains even if this card leaves the field or the monster becomes unaffected by card effects.) When this face-up card is sent to the Graveyard: You can target 1 of your banished Dragon-Type monsters; Special Summon that target. You can only control 1 face-up "Castle of Dragon Souls".

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Target 1 face-up Effect Monster on the field; that target's effects are negated, also that target cannot attack. When that target is destroyed, destroy this card.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Activate 1 or both of these effects (simultaneously). // * When an opponent's monster attacks: Target the attacking monster; change that target to Defense Position. // * Target 1 face-up monster you control; equip this card to that target. It gains 500 ATK.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Activate only by discarding 1 card when you take Battle Damage. Special Summon, in Attack Position, 1 monster from your Deck with ATK equal to or less than the Battle Damage you took.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Activate this card by targeting 1 monster in your Graveyard; Special Summon that target in face-up Attack Position. When this card leaves the field, destroy that target. When that target is destroyed, destroy this card.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: Target 1 monster on the field; return that target to the hand.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: If you control a face-up Level 7 or higher Normal Monster, when a monster would be Summoned OR a Spell/Trap Card is activated: Negate the Summon or activation, and destroy that card.

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value: 1 Tuner + 1 or more non-Tuner Normal Monsters // When this card is Special Summoned: Dragon-Type monsters you currently control cannot be targeted or destroyed by card effects until the end of the next turn. Once per turn, during your Standby Phase: You can target 1 Normal Monster in your Graveyard; Special Summon that target.
